    <note>Zhu(1) Yanmei [534] Bohu's [528] son. His wife, Sun(1) Shi, was the daughter of his mother's younger brother, Sun(1) Yanqing [3787]. His son-in-law, Liang(1) Qingzu [3557], was the grandson of Liang(1) Yanshen [3565]. Details on foreign trade in Huating (i.e., territory of modern Shanghai). SHY:ZG, 42.39a-39b, 69.17a; Sun Di, Daquanji, 58.1a; Sun Di, WJ, 34.1a. See Sun Di, 56.1a for identification as a Peiguo Zhu.</note>
